headline: Super Bowl LX's Super Schools Scores Big for Bay Area Students
summary: As big game excitement builds across the Bay Area, GENYOUth, the national nonprofit organization dedicated to helping schoolchildren thrive by living well-nourished and physically active lives, today celebrated the successful completion of its Super Schools community initiative at Grass Valley Elementary School in Oakland. headline: PG&E Accelerating Home Electrification for Customers via SPAN Edge
summary: Pacific Gas and Electric Company (PG&E) today announced a strategic collaboration with SPAN to deploy the company's SPAN Edge solution to help customers electrify their homes more affordably and efficiently.

headline: Lockheed Martin Balances Defense Growth And New Wildfire Technology Venture
summary: Lockheed Martin (NYSE:LMT) secured a Foreign Military Sales contract to supply IRST21 Legion-ES infrared sensing systems to Taiwan's Air Force, making Taiwan the first international partner for this technology. The company also launched EMBERPOINT LLC, a new wildfire detection and response venture with PG&E, Salesforce, and Wells Fargo.
